    "description": "<br><br>扮演帝欧，这是一个灵感来自希腊神话中的老英雄，如阿基里斯、赫克托尔和珀尔修斯的年轻指挥官。他使用长矛、利剑和盾牌诛杀成千上万攻击伊萨卡市的怪物。帝欧还有待发现他真正的力量，他有各种各样的装备可以使用，有神一般的力量可以召唤，有整个新的军队可征召投入战斗。这是一场为了人类命运的战争。<br> <br>试图突破你的防御的怪物数量众多，千奇百怪。你需要仔细考虑作战战术和力量平衡，特别是在与传奇老板打交道时。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479810/extras/31a3ab414666dcd28feca93ca614dc70.webp?t=1741094636\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br>最重要的目标是不要让敌人通过大门。抗战希腊神话中的野兽和传奇部落。他们会用尽全力来突破你的队伍，打破防线。<br> <br>在战斗中，你必须率领军队，想出正确的策略来面对不同敌人<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479810/extras/0cbcaf6cbfef717ec5cc18235b29a1bf.poster.avif?t=1741094636\" width=616 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479810/extras/0cbcaf6cbfef717ec5cc18235b29a1bf.webm?t=1741094636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479810/extras/864a66f1c02e7a57f9e5384eaa4e3d9f.webp?t=1741094636\" width=616 height=40 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479810/extras/efdb3edd5a75c66758e51d2f6e94b1a4.webp?t=1741094636\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br>世间的平凡武器不足以击退强大怪物的攻击。帝欧需要具有致命力量的武器，由神灵亲自祝福的器物。<br>除了排兵布阵，你还需要通过战斗升级他们，以匹配更强大和更不寻常的敌人。经典的技能树升级系统与战争技术相结合，提供所需的通用性。改变它们将打开战术选择，让你的防御者消灭不断变化的一波波怪物。<br>组合技能，打造你自己的杀手锏，成为敌人的强大对手。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479810/extras/8c963d5adda195650a716d44c398064f.poster.avif?t=1741094636\" width=616 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479810/extras/8c963d5adda195650a716d44c398064f.webm?t=1741094636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479810/extras/864a66f1c02e7a57f9e5384eaa4e3d9f.webp?t=1741094636\" width=616 height=40 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479810/extras/97ea0321cce25c56c5d47f3f31c11127.webp?t=1741094636\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br>你的敌人是来自希腊神话的野兽和传奇部族，他们从开天辟地以来就与人类发生冲突，长期以来一直想消灭他们。死者军团发动了这场战争，聚集军队，大肆袭击伊萨卡。来自各地的野兽和怪物趁机推进他们的力量。<br>特别注意老大们。它们是传说中的生物，给人类带来了很多痛苦。现在，他们将用鲁莽的原始力量来突破我们的防御。<br>阻止他们破坏我们的家园和不惜任何代价杀害我们的人民。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479810/extras/8890ec0509d9306fd25efc5720d7eeb5.poster.avif?t=1741094636\" width=616 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479810/extras/8890ec0509d9306fd25efc5720d7eeb5.webm?t=1741094636\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479810/extras/864a66f1c02e7a57f9e5384eaa4e3d9f.webp?t=1741094636\" width=616 height=40 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479810/extras/47669de947bd7365e24ad4d87272e60f.webp?t=1741094636\" width=616 height=55 /></span><br>特洛伊战争结束了。<br>伊萨卡国王奥德赛因为特洛伊木马诡计成为传奇。从特洛伊回来后，奥德赛重新获得了伊萨卡的王位，但和平并没有持续很长时间...<br>一个意想不到的事件导致奥德赛死在他的私生子手中。这一事件揭示了一个关键秘密，把无数怪物带到了到伊萨卡的大门。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479810/extras/94691be8152d02a7efc0caec055c407e.avif?t=1741094636\" width=616 height=338 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1479810/extras/864a66f1c02e7a57f9e5384eaa4e3d9f.webp?t=1741094636\" width=616 height=40 /></span><br><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>超过40个ARPG遭遇塔防的等级。<br></li><li>超过150种类型的怪物与数百个变种。<br></li><li>来自原始希腊神话的许多老大，包括地狱犬、九头蛇，蛇发女妖、牛头人等。<br></li><li>大量道具供你在无尽的狩猎中收集和装备。<br></li><li>各种军队，有几十个特殊技能，可启用无数战略。<br></li><li>还有更多与成就系统密切相关的秘密等待被发现。</li></ul>",
